Subject: [PATCH] ethtool always report port is TP on tg3
Reference: 170869
Is-Mainline: 2.6.17

Even with fiber cards ethtool reports that the connected port is TP,
the patch fix this.

Signed-off-by: Karsten Keil <kkeil@suse.de>
---

